com.deezer.sdk.network.request.event

Class DeezerError

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.deezer.sdk.network.request.event.DeezerError
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class DeezerError
extends Exception
    Encapsulation of a Deezer Error: a Deezer request that could not be fulfilled. Error codes are detailled on Deezer SDK web site.
    See Also:
    Deezer SDK docs, Serialized Form
